df_e <- as_tibble(election_2012)
df_e %>% 
  filter(!is.na(nominal_list)) %>%
  group_by(state_code)
df_e %>% 
  filter(!is.na(nominal_list)) %>%
  group_by(state_code)  %>%
  summarize(total_vote = sum(total) / sum(nominal_list) ) 
df_e %>% 
  filter(polling_type!="S") %>%
  group_by(state_code)  %>%
  summarize(total_vote = sum(total) / sum(nominal_list) ) %>%
  arrange(desc(total_vote))
